# Trade-offs

When multiple valid approaches exist, **do not choose silently**.

1. Name the decision
2. List Option A and Option B with pros/cons
3. State default recommendation
4. Note override: `PRIORITY = COST | SPEED | QUALITY | SIMPLICITY | CONSISTENCY | AVAILABILITY`

Load skill `system-design-tradeoffs` for full template and matrices.

Apply for: caching, database choice, sync vs async, SSR vs CSR, monolith vs services, agent autonomy, model tier selection.
